snippet.title: Best VGM 1456 - Silent Hill - Not Tomorrow (Lisa's Fate)
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 1623 - http://youtu.be/MYNeu0cZ3NE

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Playstation
Silent Hill (1999)
Lisa's Fate
Akira Yamaoka
